      {
        "id": "row-tip2",
        "cells": [
          1
        ],
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "col-tip2",
            "contents": [
              {
                "id": "heading-tip2",
                "type": "heading",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "0px 40px 16px",
                  "headingType": "h2",
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "fontSize": "24px",
                  "color": "#D4AF37",
                  "fontFamily": {
                    "label": "Cormorant Garamond",
                    "value": "'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif",
                    "url": "https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant Garamond:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
                  },
                  "textAlign": "left",
                  "lineHeight": "130%",
                  "text": "#2: Get Crystal Clear on \"All-Inclusive\"",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "text-tip2-1",
                "type": "text",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "0px 40px 12px",
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A4A4A;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;margin:0;\">Every venue defines \"all-inclusive\" differently, and this is exactly where hidden costs love to hide. When you're touring venues (including ours!), worth asking specifically:</p>",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "text-tip2-2",
                "type": "text",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "0px 40px 8px",
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A4A4A;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;margin:0;\">• <strong>What's included in your base price vs. what costs extra?</strong></p>",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "text-tip2-3",
                "type": "text",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "0px 40px 8px",
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A4A4A;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;margin:0;\">• <strong>Are linens included, or do you rent them separately?</strong></p>",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "text-tip2-4",
                "type": "text",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "0px 40px 8px",
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A4A4A;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;margin:0;\">• <strong>Is there a day-of coordinator included?</strong></p>",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "text-tip2-5",
                "type": "text",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "0px 40px 8px",
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A4A4A;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;margin:0;\">• <strong>Will there be any surprise charges?</strong> (Ceremony fees, Hidden Surcharges, Cleaning fees)</p>",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "text-tip2-6",
                "type": "text",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "16px 40px 30px",
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A4A4A;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;margin:0;\">At Cameron Estate, our per-person proposal covers all of the above. No separate venue rental fee. No gotchas. One clear number.<br/>At the end of your tour we will present you with a clear proposal so you know exactly what investment is required for your perfect day at Cameron Estate Inn.</p>",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              }
            ],
            "values": {}
          }
